ivardefs.name: code
ivardefs.desc: Code that identifies the type of response to the message - whether it was successful or not, and whether it should be resent or not.

ivardefs.name: details
ivardefs.desc: Full details of any issues found in the message.

ivardefs.name: identifier
ivardefs.desc: The MessageHeader.id of the message to which this message is a response.

properties.desc: Information about the message that this message is a response to.  Only present if this message is a response.
